# 2026-05-18 16:07:03.059140
+We have two issues after the latest refactoring:
+
+1. RehabPage.js uses useContext(AppStateContext) but the static arrays MORNING_ROUTINE and EVENING_ROUTINE are not provided by the context. This causes "Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'map')" at RoutineList. Fix: import MORNING_ROUTINE and EVENING_ROUTINE directly from '../../config/constants.js' in RehabPage.js.
+
+2. PWA manifest requests icon-192.png and icon-512.png, which are missing (404). Create minimal placeholder icons (a simple green circle or square) as inline SVG references in manifest.json, or generate tiny valid PNGs using inline data URIs. Also ensure the app has a favicon to avoid 404.
+
+All existing functionality must be preserved.

